Invocation Name: my mickey vacation tips
des:
Are you planning a Walt Disney World vacation with the Dream Designers at My Mickey Vacation Travel? With our expertise, we take the stress out of planning what could otherwise be an overwhelming vacation experience. 

My Mickey Vacation Tips is provided to our guests as a way to receive a new daily tip each day to make your vacation even more magical. Tips include ways to enjoy the parks, resorts, dining, attractions, and yes, even shopping.

To book your vacation with My Mickey Vacation Travel, visit us at http://mymickeyvacation.com
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
